    {
      "allowLineSplit": true,
      "content": "An enlarged initial letter — the drop cap — has marked the opening of chapters and stanzas since illuminated manuscripts. The letter descends into the column, commanding two to five lines of body text, while the remaining characters of the first word wrap around it.",
